text: Daria Ryzhkova (8 February 1995) is a Russian water polo player. She competed for the Russian national team at the 2014 Women's European Water Polo Championship, and 2017 World Aquatics Championships ==See also== * List of World Aquatics Championships medalists in water polo ==References== ==External links== * * Daria Ryzhkova Category:Russian female water polo players Category:1995 births Category:World Aquatics Championships medalists in water polo Category:Living people
